Baldwin Family[]

The Baldwin Family is a family of Actors and Actresses that includes the four acting siblings Alec, Daniel, William and Stephen, who are known collectively as the Baldwin brothers and their wives and children. The Baldwin familys patrilineal line traces to a Richard Baldwin, who lived in England, c. the 1500s. Through their father Alexander Rae Baldwin Jr., the Baldwins are descended from the Mayflower passenger John Howland. The four brothers are therefore the 13th generation of their family to be born in North America.

The Cuomo Family is an American political, business and performer family. It includes Mario Cuomo and Matilda Cuomo (ne Raffa) and their five children: Margaret, Andrew, Maria, Madeline, and Christopher. Mario Cuomo had served as governor of New York which brought their family to fame, his son Andrew is a businessman who is the CEO of the Walt Disney Company and his son Chris is a performer and journalist. The daughters and wives of Andrew and Chris are all actresses who performed in Disney Media.

Presley[]

The Presley Family is a family of entertainers that was founded by Elvis Presley, a musician who is dubbed the "King of Rock and Roll", he is regarded as one of the most significant cultural figures of the 20th century. His energized interpretations of songs and sexually provocative performance style, combined with a singularly potent mix of influences across color lines during a transformative era in race relations, led him to both great success and initial controversy. The family consists of Elvis himself, his wife, his daughter and granddaughter.

This arrangement was accepted by both ladies, and by all four of his children by his first wife. The family then adopted a girl, Arpita Khan, who was formally adopted by Helen and raised amid the entire family in their family home in Galaxy Apartments, Bandra Bandstand, Mumbai. Eventually,all of the children of Salim Khan had married and had children as the daughter he adopted with Helen remained single and childless. His maternal Granddaughter, Alizeh Agnihorti had married Prince August Pahlavi which resulted in the Khan Family becoming a connected family of the Pahlavi Dynasty.

Wolfhard[]

The Wolfhard Family, other than the Hu family is another family of actors and actresses that is involved in the Anime Distribution industry of Hawaii. The Family was founded by Eric Wolfhard who is a Historical Researcher, Monarchist Politician who is a member of the Hawaiian Nationalist Monarchist Party, the owner of Sentai Filmworks and an anime VA and his wife Mary Jolivet who is related to American Silent film actresses.
